Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:19.32,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:253483,259322}Ever since I teamed up with you, I can organize my thoughts a lot better, Spex. Thank you.{NOTE:ピントと組んでから僕自分の考えをうまく整理できて感謝してるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:27.12,Default,Spex,1,1,0,,{TIME:259322,267121}Me too. I'm a bit weak but I'm glad I have you, Hyoro. You're kind to everyone and you have a strong backbone.{NOTE:ほうほう。僕もちょっと気弱だけどみんなに優しくて芯のあるヒョロさんと組めてうれしいゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:34.04,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:267121,274045}A Velocidrome isn't bad, but if we want to face\Nthe Ebon Riders, another Monstie will come in handy.{NOTE:ドスランポスも悪くないオトモンだがブラックライダーズ相手には次のオトモンも手に入れたいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.34,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:274045,277340}Well said, Beats.{NOTE:そうっすよねビーツ先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:42.92,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:277340,282929}Remember, there are still all sorts of things I have to teach you.{NOTE:お前にはまだまだ俺が教えてやらなきゃいけないことが山のようにあるからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:48.35,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:282929,288351}Aren't you exaggerating?\NI feel like I'm catching up to you.{NOTE:いや～自分そろそろビーツ先輩なしでも大丈夫じゃないっすかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.72,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:288351,290728}What did you say?{NOTE:何だと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.65,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:299237,300655}What's wrong, Nariki!?{NOTE:どうした!?ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:04.78,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:300655,304784}Beats! I found an egg!{NOTE:ビーツ先輩！卵見つけたっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.87,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:305993,307870}Master Anvis.{NOTE:アンヴィスさま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.66,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:307870,311666}What's going to happen with Noir?{NOTE:ノワルはどうなるのでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.33,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:311666,315336}You knew this would happen and yet you still carried on with the rite?{NOTE:ああなると分かっていて儀式を行ったのですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:19.42,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:315336,319423}Do you have a problem with my methods?{NOTE:私のやったことに異を挟むのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:24.88,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:319423,324887}I am Anvis, and I possess power that surpasses every Rider.{NOTE:私はあらゆるライダーを超越したライダーアンヴィスなのだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:29.51,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:324887,329517}Get out of my sight. Don't come back until I give you my instruction.{NOTE:下がれ。追って沙汰あるまでここには来なくてよい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:38.44,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:334397,338442}Those Hakum village brats are in for a surprise.{NOTE:ハクム村のやつらいきなり行って驚かしてやるぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.69,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:338442,340695}Are you sure about that?{NOTE:それはどうかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.90,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:340695,342905}What? You guys!{NOTE:何だ？お前ら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.57,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:342905,345575}We expected you to come here.{NOTE:ﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞが来るのを待っていたのさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.66,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:346033,348661}Well, that saves me the effort of finding you.{NOTE:そいつはご苦労なこった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.87,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:348661,350872}We're not gonna let you do as you please!{NOTE:もうお前たちの勝手にはさせない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.45,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:353249,355459}Eek!{NOTE:ヒィ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.17,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:355459,358170}Heheh! How are you going to stop me?{NOTE:ヘヘヘ！どうするってんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.54,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:359463,361549}I'll take you on.{NOTE:私が相手をします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:05.63,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:361549,365636}Oh? How have you been, little girl?{NOTE:ほう…お嬢ちゃん、元気になったのかよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.01,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:365636,367013}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.68,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:367013,368683}Barioth!{NOTE:ベリオロス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.43,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:370182,371434}Let's go, Frostfang.{NOTE:いきましょうヒョウガ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:20.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:376188,380318}Hmm… his Deviljho seems to be stronger.{NOTE:うーむイビルジョーはやはり強そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:24.69,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:380318,384697}I don't think Avinia will lose,\Nbut I don't think it'll be easy either.{NOTE:アユリアの希望とはいえこのままじゃまずそうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:384697,385907}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.28,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:388075,389285}Rathian!{NOTE:リオレイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.04,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:394373,397043}Sync Ride!{NOTE:シンクライド！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.97,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:411659,413976}That's not fair, you cowards!{NOTE:ひきょうだぞお前たち！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.43,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:413976,417438}A Rider's power lies in the strength of their kinship.{NOTE:俺たちライダーの力は絆の力だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:02.27,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:417438,422276}Our true power comes from combining everyone's power!{NOTE:みんなの力を合わせた力が俺たちの本当の力なんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.48,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:423027,425488}Geez… I'll let you go for today.{NOTE:今日はこの辺にしておいてやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.99,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:425488,427990}But I'll be back!{NOTE:覚えてろよ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.53,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:430743,433537}O' holy Kinship Stone…{NOTE:聖なる絆石よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.83,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:433537,436832}…bind thou together our's and these slumbering souls.{NOTE:われと眠りしみ霊の絆を結びたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.37,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:436832,439377}And now, the moment of new life:{NOTE:いざ新生の時。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.21,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:439377,441212}Awaken!{NOTE:目覚めよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.05,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:446926,449053}It's a Brachydios!{NOTE:ブラキディオスっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.51,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:449053,450513}Right on!{NOTE:やったな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.97,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:450513,451973}Awesome, Nariki!{NOTE:すごいよ、ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.85,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:453349,454850}It's so cute…{NOTE:カワイイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.85,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:454850,457853}I'll call this little fella "Blow".{NOTE:この子の名前はブローに決めたっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.98,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:457853,460982}Very nice! That's a good name, Nariki.{NOTE:うむ。いい名前だな、ナリキ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:47.53,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:460982,467530}Deepen your kinship with Brachydios\Nas you deepened it with your Velocidrome.{NOTE:ドスランポスと絆を深めたようにブラキディオスともしっかり絆を深めていけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.44,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:467530,469448}Okay! Roger that!{NOTE:はい！了解っす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.24,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:473035,476247}Master Gale. What's going to happen now?{NOTE:ゲイルさま。この後どうなるんすかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:06.46,Default,Gale,1,1,0,,{TIME:478207,486465}Nuts. I don't know Master Anvis's true goal even though\NI've worked here with you for a while now.{NOTE:ナッツ。お前とはここで組んでしばらくたつがアンヴィスさまの本当の目的は俺にもよく分からないのさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.38,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:486465,490386}I think it's to make the power of the Sync Ride stronger…?{NOTE:シンクライドの力をより強くするって話は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:490386,491303}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:19.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:491303,499020}It seems that the Ebon Riders' Sync Ride originates from a ritual done in a certain village of Riders.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズの編み出したシンクライドももともとはあるライダー村で行われていた儀式から想を得たものらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.35,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:499020,501355}I see, I see.{NOTE:ほうほう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:26.48,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:501355,506485}It may even be related to the rite performed on Noir.{NOTE:姉さんに施した儀式もそれと関係があるのかもな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:31.53,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:506485,511532}Do you want that power too, Master Gale?{NOTE:ゲイルさまも欲しいっすか？その力。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.74,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:511532,515745}Nuts. Why do you think I've joined the Ebon Riders?{NOTE:ナッツ。俺が何でﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞに入っていると思う？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:39.54,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:515745,519540}Ah… I'm sorry I asked a bad question…{NOTE:あっ…すいませんやぼな質問。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.25,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:519540,522251}Gale, do you have a moment?{NOTE:ゲイル。ちょっといいかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:522251,524628}What's up, Sis?{NOTE:何すか？姉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:53.63,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:527506,533637}The reason I gathered you all here is because Avinia wanted to tell you something.{NOTE:皆に集まってもらったのはアユリアから皆に話したいことがあるそうじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:09:02.68,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:536057,542688}I deeply apologize for all the inconveniences I've caused for you all.{NOTE:皆さん。あらためましてこのたびは色々ご迷惑をお掛けして申し訳ありませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:06.06,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:542688,546067}But you didn't do anything wrong, Avinia.\NSo why apologize?{NOTE:気にするな。アユリアは悪くない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.94,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:546067,547943}Thank you, Navirou.{NOTE:ありがとう。ナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:14.40,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:547943,554408}But I don't think the Ebon Riders kidnapping me was a coincidence.{NOTE:でも今回私がﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞに誘拐されたことは偶然ではないと思っています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:19.28,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:554992,559288}Is it really that strange that I've decided\Nto leave the Ebon Riders?{NOTE:あたしがブラックライダーズを抜けるのがそんなに不思議かい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:23.29,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:559288,563292}I guess. But why did you tell me about it?{NOTE:それもあるんすけど俺に言っちゃっていいんすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.62,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:563292,566629}Because I feel like you're the only one\Nwho will understand.{NOTE:何で話すかっていうと分かるのさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:30.25,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:566629,570257}You're also pretty disgusted with all of this, aren't you?{NOTE:あんたがブラックライダーズに愛想を尽かしているのがね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.09,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:570257,572093}How did you know…?{NOTE:マジっすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.09,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:572093,575096}Right on mark, huh? Call it woman's intuition.{NOTE:図星だろ？女の勘さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.84,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:575096,576847}I can't deny that.{NOTE:それはそれは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:41.18,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:576847,581185}You joined the Ebon Riders with your own ulterior motives, didn't you?{NOTE:お前も腹に一物あってﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞに参加しているんだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.85,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:581185,582853}You're awfully transparent.{NOTE:見え見えだったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.94,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:582853,585940}Oh? You've seen through me for that long?{NOTE:あらら？そんなふうに見えました？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:50.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:585940,590402}Your ability to read people is scary, Sis.{NOTE:怖いな～シャドウの姉さんは何でもお見通しですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:54.03,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:590402,594031}Hah. Don't try to flatter me.{NOTE:フン…せいぜいねこをかぶってるがいいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.03,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:596408,600037}I can't eat so many donuts at once…{NOTE:もうそんなにドーナツは食べられないぞ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.41,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:603582,606418}Lute… can you sleep?{NOTE:リュート眠れないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:11.38,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:606418,611382}No. I'm thinking about what Avinia said.{NOTE:ああ。アユリアの話考えてたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.26,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:611382,614260}About the Ebon Riders' goal?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズの目的？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.34,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:614260,617346}Yeah… That too.{NOTE:もちろんそれもあるけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:22.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:617346,622810}But also about how Avinia has just seemed really sad ever since I met her.{NOTE:最初会ったときからアユリアって悲しそうだったんだよな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:29.60,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:625688,629608}I'm glad I get along with you, Cheval.{NOTE:俺とシュヴァルで仲良くしてやらなきゃな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.19,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:629608,631193}Yeah, me too.{NOTE:そうだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:36.65,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:631193,636657}Yes, I'm hungry. Thank you for the donuts…{NOTE:うむおなかがすいてきた。食べるぞ～ドーナツ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:47.50,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:640786,647501}A lot has happened. But if it hadn't, we wouldn't have met each other.{NOTE:色々あるけど色々なかったら私はアユリアに会うことなかったのよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.71,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:647501,649712}I suppose so.{NOTE:そうですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.83,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:649712,651839}Fate is such a strange thing.{NOTE:運命って不思議よね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:58.63,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:651839,658639}If Manelger hadn't modified me,\NI wouldn't have met everyone in the Numbers.{NOTE:私もマネルガーに改造されてなかったらナンバーズの皆に出会わなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:04.72,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:658639,664727}I would've never guessed that bubbly, little Navirou had such a dark past.{NOTE:あんなに明るいナビルーにもそんな過去があったなんて思いもしませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:10.81,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:664727,670816}I don't have any regrets, though. We'll just keep moving forward.{NOTE:後悔なんてしてないけどね。前に進むだけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.10,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:670816,672109}Well said.{NOTE:ですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.19,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:672109,674195}Now, let's get some sleep.{NOTE:そろそろ寝ましょうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.03,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:674195,676030}We have to get up early tomorrow.{NOTE:あしたも早いわ。}
