Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:39.05,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:696008,699053}Anvis…{NOTE:アンヴィスを}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.55,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:699053,700554}…I'll stop you.{NOTE:止める！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:02.49,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:719156,722493}At last you revealed your true nature.{NOTE:とうとう本性を現しおったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.29,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:724328,728290}It's just like I told you, Master Anvis.{NOTE:アンヴィスさまお知らせしたとおりでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.25,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:728290,731252}Master Gale is a traitor.{NOTE:ゲイルさまは裏切り者です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.79,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:731252,732795}Nuts…?{NOTE:ナッツ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.63,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:734964,737633}Actually, I didn't tell you…{NOTE:実はお伝えしていなかったことが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:22.17,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:737633,742179}…but I am a faithful subordinate\Nwho reports directly to Master Anvis.{NOTE:このナッツはアンヴィスさま直属の忠実な部下でありまして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:27.01,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:742179,747017}Your daily actions were reported to Master Anvis, one by one.{NOTE:ゲイルさまの日頃の動向は逐一アンヴィスさまに報告しておりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:34.60,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:749478,754608}Gale. I didn't trust you right from the beginning.{NOTE:ゲイルよ。私はお前を最初から信じていなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.69,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:754608,756694}Oh, really?{NOTE:そうでしたか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:40.23,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:756694,760239}You inherit the rite of Kuang village.{NOTE:お前はクアン村の儀式を受け継ぐ者だろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.99,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:760239,763993}How could you think…{NOTE:すっかり見違えたぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:48.03,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:763993,768038}…that you would ever get what you wanted?{NOTE:欲しいものが自分の手中にすでにあったとはな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.08,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:772126,774086}Put him in jail.{NOTE:ろうに入れておけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.79,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:777381,778799}Dan?{NOTE:ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:03.09,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:778799,783095}Can Nariki Ride On his new Monstie already?{NOTE:ナリキの新しいオトモンもうライドオンできるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.22,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:783095,784221}Yeah.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:07.80,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:784221,787808}It's a little early, but we thought to do a mock-fight with Mille.{NOTE:せっかくだからミルと模擬戦をやろうと思ってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.14,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:787808,791145}Nariki's new Monstie is amazing!{NOTE:ナリキの新しいオトモンすごいぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.93,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:791145,793939}All right! Are you two ready?{NOTE:よし！２人とも準備はいいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:17.27,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:793939,797276}But this isn't a real fight.\NKinship Techniques are prohibited.{NOTE:あくまで模擬戦。絆技は禁止だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.77,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:797276,798777}– Okay!\N– Okay!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.19,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:798777,800195}All right, begin!{NOTE:それでは始め！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.82,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:800779,801822}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.95,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:803824,804950}Seregios!{NOTE:セルレギオス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.82,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:805784,806827}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.20,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:808912,810205}Brachydios!{NOTE:ブラキディオス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.30,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:820591,822301}A Brachydios!?{NOTE:ブラキディオス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.30,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:822301,824303}You've got an awesome Monstie.{NOTE:すごいのを手に入れたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:48.51,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:824303,828515}It may be a mock-fight, but I still won't hold back.{NOTE:ミル先輩模！擬戦だからって手加減しないっすよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.64,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:828515,831643}Save those lines for after the fight.{NOTE:そのせりふは私に勝ってから言いなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.27,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:831643,834271}This armor looks cool, don't you think?{NOTE:この装備カッコイイでしょ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.81,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:834271,836815}An opening! Split Claw!{NOTE:隙あり！千裂爪！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.27,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:839318,841278}Great Tackle!{NOTE:グレートタックル！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.90,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:841278,842905}Ah! Too fast!{NOTE:うわ！速い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.11,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:842905,846116}As expected, Brachydios has awesome power.{NOTE:さすがにブラキディオスはすごいパワーね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:10.32,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:846116,850329}That Nariki… He hasn't strengthened his ties with Blow yet?{NOTE:ナリキのやつまだブローとの絆が築けてないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.58,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:850329,853582}Nope. He can't handle him at all yet.{NOTE:うん。うまく力を引き出せていないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.12,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:855667,857127}What's wrong, Blow?{NOTE:どうした？ブロー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.08,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:857127,859088}What are you doing?{NOTE:お前こんなもんじゃないだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.84,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:859088,862841}Calm down, Nariki! Don't let Blow's power overwhelm you.{NOTE:落ち着けナリキ！ブローのパワーに振り回されるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.76,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:865886,868764}You're 100 years too young beat me in a fight.{NOTE:あたしに勝とうなんて100年早いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.72,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:868764,872726}Damn! Let's try a Kinship Technique!{NOTE:くっそ～！よし絆技でけりをつける！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.68,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:872726,875687}Blast Blow!{NOTE:ブラキブラストブロー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.60,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:875687,876605}Huh?{NOTE:あれ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.65,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:876605,879650}I told you… 100 years too young!{NOTE:だ～か～ら～…100年早いって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:42.90,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:881527,882903}That hurts…!{NOTE:いって～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.61,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:882903,884613}All right, stop!{NOTE:よしそこまで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.11,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:887741,889118}What the hell was that?{NOTE:バカじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.74,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:889118,892746}Why were you trying to use Kinship Technique in a mock-fight?{NOTE:何で模擬戦で絆技出そうとするわけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.16,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:892746,894164}Sorry…{NOTE:すんません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:15:00.01,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:894164,900011}Nariki. Brachydios is a great Monstie,\Nbut there's no point if you don't have any kinship.{NOTE:ナリキ。ブラキディオスはすごいオトモンだが絆がなけりゃ意味がないぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.71,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:900011,902714}You've got to deepen your bond more.{NOTE:もっと絆を深めなきゃ駄目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:07.21,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:902714,907219}The Ebon Riders are strong,\Nbut we put up a good fight, too.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズは強いけど俺たちもなかなかのもんじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.84,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:907219,908846}You're right.{NOTE:そうだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:13.80,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:908846,913809}Besides we don't just have individual power,\Nwe also have the power of our kinship combined.{NOTE:俺たちには一人一人の力以外に絆の力がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:18.48,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:913809,918480}{\fad(0,200)}Yeah, so even if all four of them were to gang up on us, we wouldn't lose.{NOTE:四天王がまとめて来ても今の俺たちなら負けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:23.69,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:919481,923694}Master Anvis. They are certainly getting stronger.{NOTE:アンヴィスさま！やつら確実に強くなってますぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:31.53,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:923694,931535}After they have gone through the rite of channeling,\Ntheir Monsties are on par with our Sync Ride.{NOTE:オトモンも伝承の儀でパワーアップしていてこっちがシンクライドして五分五分って感じでヤバいですぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.74,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:932661,934746}I don't like it…{NOTE:気に入らないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.37,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:934746,936373}Hm?{NOTE:うん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:40.54,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:936373,940544}The Ebon Riders were supposed to be overwhelmingly strong Riders, right?{NOTE:ﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞは圧倒的に強いﾗｲﾀﾞｰだったんじゃないのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:44.84,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:940544,944840}Shadow! Watch your tongue before Master Anvis.{NOTE:シャドウ！アンヴィスさまに口答えはやめろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.92,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:944840,946925}Where's Gale?{NOTE:ゲイルはどこに行ったのさ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.64,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:950929,953640}I don't like your attitude either.{NOTE:あんたたちの態度も気に入らないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.64,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:953640,955642}What did you say?{NOTE:今何と言いました？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:16:00.39,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:955642,960397}Hahaha! Interesting. What are you trying to say?{NOTE:ウッハッハッハ！面白い。だったらどうだというんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.98,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:960397,962983}Thanks to your rite, Noir—{NOTE:あんたたちの儀式でノワルは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.61,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:962983,964610}Doesn't matter.{NOTE:くだらん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:08.44,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:964610,968447}I've had it! Ride On! Nargacuga!{NOTE:ふざけんな！ライドオン！ナルガクルガ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:12.99,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:971867,972993}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.37,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:974077,975370}Kushala Daora!{NOTE:クシャルダオラ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.12,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:982503,984129}Sync Ride!{NOTE:シンクライド！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:46.36,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:999770,1006360}I can defeat worthless scum like you even without Sync Ride. It's easy, like taking a candy from a baby.{NOTE:貴様ごときはシンクライドせずとも倒せる。赤子の手をひねるようなものよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.07,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008946,1011073}Capture Shadow! {NOTE:シャドウを捕らえよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.78,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011073,1013784}Uh-oh, what a shame.{NOTE:あ～あしょうがねえな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.70,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013784,1016703}You bark was bigger than your bite.{NOTE:弱い犬ほどよく吠えるってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.62,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016703,1020624}How unlady-like. Certainly not beautiful at all.{NOTE:美しくない。まったくもって美しくない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.66,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021708,1023669}Gale betrayed me.{NOTE:ゲイルは裏切った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.83,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023669,1025837}What?! Unbelievable!{NOTE:何ということでしょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:10.63,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025837,1030634}Master Anvis. Please let me get rid of him.{NOTE:アンヴィスさま。やつの始末はどうぞこのマッドにお任せください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:15.47,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030634,1035472}The four Ebon Riders suddenly became just two!? Hahaha!{NOTE:四天王が二天王になっちまった！ハッハッハッハ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.51,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035472,1038517}Heh. Things have gotten interesting.{NOTE:フッ…面白い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:25.31,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039184,1045315}I knew Gale was in a position\Nto know the rite of overlapping.{NOTE:ゲイルが重ね合わせの儀のまつりごとを知る立場であることは分かっていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.73,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1045315,1046733}Huh?!{NOTE:あっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:30.02,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046733,1050028}Now I have all the pieces regarding the rite.{NOTE:儀式のための駒は完全に揃った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.82,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050028,1052823}All there's left to do is to put them together.{NOTE:あとは集めればよいだけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:37.11,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052823,1057119}Will you lend me your strength? Wrath!? Mad!?{NOTE:力を貸してくれるか？ラースマッド。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.78,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1057119,1058787}Yes sir!{NOTE:はっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059788,1061373}Let's see…{NOTE:え～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.79,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061373,1064793}Looks like everyone's here.{NOTE:みんなに集まってもらったのはほかでもない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:49.59,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064793,1069590}Every now and then, it's good to drop the pretense…{NOTE:たまにはざっくばらんに腹を割って気楽に忖度なく…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069590,1072551}…and have a honest talk while eating a pair of donuts.{NOTE:…ドーナツでも食べながら話でもしようかと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.42,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1072551,1074428}{NOTE:だー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:59.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074428,1079266}You know what? Why not?\NWe've all been having a pretty rough time lately.{NOTE:でもさ確かにずっと大変だったからたまにはいいかもな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.51,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079266,1080517}That's true.{NOTE:そうだよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.10,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080517,1082102}I think so, too.{NOTE:僕もそう思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.85,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082102,1085856}There are plenty of things I'd like to ask you, Avinia.{NOTE:あたしもアユリアに聞きたいこと結構あるのよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.94,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085856,1086940}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:13.19,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086940,1093196}I also want to ask my seniors how to deepen my kinship with my Monsties.{NOTE:自分もオトモンともっと絆を深めるにはどうしたらいいか先輩たちに聞きたいっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:18.20,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093196,1098201}Yeah. Looks like somebody's motivated.\NI'll evaluate that attitude.{NOTE:あっ。やる気が前面に出てきたな。その姿勢評価するぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.00,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102372,1105000}Recently it's just seemed like one problem after another.{NOTE:大変なことになったのう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:28.67,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105000,1108670}A lot things happen when you live for a long time.{NOTE:長く生きていると色々なことがあるものじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:32.96,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108670,1112966}It is a bit regrettable that we have to rely on the younger generation.{NOTE:若者に頼るしかないとは口惜しいのぉ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.92,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112966,1115927}Let's just do what we can.{NOTE:わしらにできることをやるしかないじゃろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.38,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115927,1118388}You're right.{NOTE:そうですな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:41.43,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118388,1121433}They're all doing well for themselves.{NOTE:彼らは本当によくやっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.81,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121433,1123810}They're good kids.{NOTE:素直な良い子たちじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.48,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123810,1126480}Can't argue there.{NOTE:うん。そう思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.40,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126855,1130400}This again!? I hate when you get like this, Lute!{NOTE:そこ！リュートのそういうとこが嫌なんだ！}
