Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.43,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159971,1163433}I'm sorry you have to put up with this, Avinia.{NOTE:ごめんねアユリア。変なとこ見せちゃって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:27.97,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163433,1167979}I had doubts about Lute and Navirou when we first met…{NOTE:最初に会ったときもリュートやナビルーの態度には疑問を持ちましたけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.69,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168605,1170691}Listen, I'm telling you,\Nyou can't do this on that leg.{NOTE:そのケガじゃ無理だって。}
