Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:56.38,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193380,1196383}Are you listening, Gale?{NOTE:聞いてるかい？ゲイル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.21,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196383,1199219}I'm sorry, Sis…{NOTE:姉さんすまない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.43,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199219,1201430}Not that it's my business, but…{NOTE:あんたにゃ関係ないさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:05.97,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201430,1205976}…you've got something complicated going on there, don't you?{NOTE:ただややこしいことには変わりないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:10.39,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205976,1210397}I tried to do the right thing, but got the opposite results.{NOTE:うまくやろうとしたのが裏目に出ちゃいまして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:16.06,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210397,1216069}I'd recommend against trying to do the right thing when you're so young.{NOTE:若いときはうまくやろうとするのはおすすめしないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.82,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216069,1217821}You're too earnest.{NOTE:真面目にやりな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.49,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219364,1222492}I'm sorry to interrupt your chat.{NOTE:皆さまご歓談中失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:27.45,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222492,1227456}Master Anvis is calling for you, Master Gale.{NOTE:アンヴィスさまがお呼びですよ。ゲイルさま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.37,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227456,1230375}Please don't look at me like that.{NOTE:そんな目で見ないでくださいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:33.83,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230375,1233837}I just did my work the best I could.{NOTE:自分は自分の仕事を一生懸命にやっただけですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.38,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233837,1236381}It's not like I don't like you, Master Gale.{NOTE:ゲイルさまが嫌いなわけじゃないですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:42.22,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236381,1242220}But Master Anvis is my boss.\NI had to watch you, Master Gale…{NOTE:ただ直接の雇い主のアンヴィスさまからゲイルさまを見張るように命令されて見張ってたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:47.05,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242220,1247058}…and of course I had no choice but to report your betrayal.{NOTE:ゲイルさまがアンヴィスさまを裏切っちゃうから報告するしかないでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.89,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250353,1252898}Why did you call me here?{NOTE:何の用ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:56.86,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252898,1256860}Bring me Avinia's Kinship Stone.{NOTE:アユリアとその絆石をここに持ってまいれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.19,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256860,1260197}Huh? Why would you ask me such thing now?{NOTE:はあ？何で俺がいまさらそんなことを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.90,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260197,1263909}Master Gale, please watch your words.{NOTE:これこれゲイルさま口が過ぎますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:07.91,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263909,1267913}If you refuse to, I'll kill the Shadow sisters.{NOTE:それができぬのならシャドウ姉妹を殺す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.29,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270123,1272292}What will you do now?{NOTE:さあどうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.92,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272292,1274920}Come on, Master Gale, give your answer.{NOTE:ささゲイルさま答えて答えて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:27.64,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280258,1287641}About my hometown… I can't tell you more about the rituals held in Kuang village.{NOTE:私の故郷…クアン村で行われていた儀式のことは詳しくお話しすることはできません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:32.18,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287641,1292187}I really don't know much about my childhood.{NOTE:私が幼いころで本当に知らないのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:39.06,Default,Avinia,1,1,0,,{TIME:1292187,1299069}The only thing I know is that, somehow, the Ebon Riders gathering Kinship Stones and the ritual are connected.{NOTE:ただ今回ブラックライダーズが絆石を集めていることと大きな関係があるのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:43.69,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299069,1303698}The Ebon Riders place their Kinship Stones on their foreheads, unlike ours.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズの絆石は俺たちと違って額にある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:48.99,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303698,1308995}And once they call "Sync Ride", their movements get much swifter.{NOTE:そして｢シンクライド｣と叫ぶと動きが鋭くなったりする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.16,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308995,1312165}Do you think any of that is importance, too?{NOTE:そのこととも関わりがあるんだね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.87,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312165,1314876}I wasn't convinced at first.{NOTE:今までは確信がありませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:22:00.13,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314876,1320131}But now that I've learned new things,\NI think I see the truth.{NOTE:でもいろんなことを知るうちに自分の中で真実が見えてきたのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:09.89,Default,Navirou,1,1,0,,{TIME:1320131,1329891}It's like not being able to know how a donut tastes\Nuntil you actually taste it with your own tongue.{NOTE:いろんな種類のドーナツをどんな味かな～って思っていて実際に口に入れて舌で味わってみて感想を言うみたいなものだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.72,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329891,1331726}No, it's not like that.{NOTE:違うと思いますが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.27,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331726,1333270}Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:17.39,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333270,1337399}Me and Ratha will definitely stop Anvis's right in his tracks!{NOTE:アンヴィスのもくろみは俺とレウスで絶対に止めてやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:18.65,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337399,1338650}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:21.48,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338650,1341486}All of us Hakum village Riders will join forces.{NOTE:俺たちハクム村のライダーが力を合わせる。}
