Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:05.57,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382193,1385572}Along with Master Anvis faithful subordinate, Nuts!{NOTE:アンヴィスさまの忠実な部下ナッツと共に！}
