Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:10.91,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387616,1390911}Ah! How scary! Master Gale is extremely scary!{NOTE:お～怖っ！ゲイルさま超怖～い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.37,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1390911,1393371}Come on, Master Gale! Be serious about this!{NOTE:さあ、ゲイルさま本気出してください！}
